{"tid":1228552,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"真係好撚嬲","createTime":"2019-06-15T17:22:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T17:23:10.000Z","uid":51275,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0de3a6d1f0cde4be7e9dcf5d6e75f52a4a4696e9","tid":1228552,"uid":51275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T17:22:05.000Z","msg":"意見不合 唔緊要<br />\n明白人各有異 想法唔同係正常<br />\n<br />\n但大家上街 為未來抗爭 為自由發聲 對抗不公義事 你唔講加油 置身度外 仲要落井下石 取笑他人既付出 <br />\n覺得全部人都係為&rdquo;錢&rdquo;而上街抗爭 <br />\n呢個說法真係好噁心 <br />\n見到「有錢收」己經想嘔<br />\n<br />\n唔係全部人都係好似你地咁 唔係所有人都有個價<br />\n我地為緊既係比錢更重要既野 咪撚用自己既小人之心度君子之腹 <br />\n<br />\n愈諗愈嬲 乜撚野上街有錢收 我屌你老母 講得出呢句說話既人 <br />\n你生而為人 我對你感到很抱歉"},{"pid":"fcc4f8cc52dc739bac1457d558d3fdfbd79e8a3e","tid":1228552,"uid":51275,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T17:22:33.000Z","msg":"好撚想嘔 呢幾日<br />\n社會上太多人形怪物"},{"pid":"6b8568e5c911b10d36a041e7892d4882f448c81d","tid":1228552,"uid":36013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T17:23:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/pvAhRcUofDk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FpvAhRcUofDk&d=YAxVOUHAW5%2FtYfR1oVoe22Z69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=a35dea10\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/pvAhRcUofDk</a>"},{"pid":"46a0beea6b39218207d0b65e5a20dc90f9649c7c","tid":1228552,"uid":105879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T17:23:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1228370\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1228370</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n入面呢班人渣全部都一樣要付出代價"}]}